{
  "texts": [
    "Several strategies have been proposed to mitigate spectral bias.",
    "Positional EncodingPositional encoding (P.E.)",
    "lifts input coordinates into a higher-dimensional space using predefined sine and cosine functions.",
    "These encoded coordinates are then used as input to a regular MLP with ReLU activations, which we refer to as the P.E.",
    "ReLU architecture."
  ]
}